zookeeper                    "/etc/confluent/dockâ€¦"    zookeeper           running             2888/tcp, 0.0.0.0:2181->2181/tcp, 3888/tcp
```

# Should see valid list of Topics been created
docker exec -it kafka1 kafka-topics --bootstrap-server kafka1:19092,kafka2:19093 --list
docker exec -it kafka2 kafka-topics --bootstrap-server kafka1:19092,kafka2:19093 --list
```
__consumer_offsets
reminders
```

